    public static class GoogleMaps.Circle
extends GoogleMaps.MapItem
    A map item that represents a circle. 
          GoogleMaps.Circle c = new GoogleMaps.Circle();
      c.lat = -3.73243;
      c.lon = -38.483414;
      c.color = Color.BLUE;
      c.filled = false;
      c.rad = 70;
